{"tid":1134672,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"繼美法軍艦後泰國軍艦駛經台灣海峽","createTime":"2019-05-01T23:20:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-02T01:36:32.000Z","uid":35790,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"cba10df873d201049e5a357bc66dd63ffcd6f0c8","tid":1134672,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T23:20:49.000Z","msg":"繼美法軍艦後泰國軍艦駛經台灣海峽<br />\n( 博訊北京時間2019年5月01日 轉載 )<br />\n    <br />\n    外國軍艦駛經台灣海峽，被大陸視為十分敏感的事件，不過，內地社交媒體今日廣傳一張船泊追踪地圖，顯示泰國海軍的「邦巴功」號護衛艦，近日駛經台灣海峽，昨日經過香港以南海域，駛往廣東湛江，這是繼美國、法國軍艦之後，再有外國的軍艦駛經台灣海峽。<br />\n    <br />\n    在微博廣傳的圖片，顯示炫號456號的「邦巴功」號護衛艦，上月28日晚在福州對開海域，駛進台灣海峽，大約沿台海中線往南行駛，之後一直沿廣東沿岸航行，昨日上午駛近香港以南海域，繼續沿西南方向行駛。<br />\n    <br />\n    「邦巴功」號護衛艦是中國製造的戰艦，根據中國053HT型護衛艦加以改良而成，1989年動工、1990年7月25日下水，1991年7月20日正式服役。這艘戰艦滿載排水量1,924噸，配備4座雙聯裝「鷹擊」反艦導彈發射裝置、1座8管「西北風」艦空導彈發射裝置、2座中國雙100毫米主砲、8座雙37毫米副砲和2座5管固定式反潛深彈發射裝置。<br />\n    <br />\n    「邦巴功」號護衛艦與納萊頌恩號護衛艦（舷號421），上月21日抵達山東青島，參與解放軍海軍70年的海上閱兵，在離開青島，邦巴功號護衛艦一路南下，穿越台灣海峽進入南海，前往湛江。​​​​ <br />\n    <br />\n    這是近日再有外國軍艦駛經台灣海峽。美國太平洋艦隊表示，上月28日派出驅逐艦「斯特西姆」號（USS Stethem）及驅逐艦「勞倫斯號」（USS William P. Lawrence），駛過台灣海峽，以展示美國建立自由開放印太地區的承諾。法國護衛艦葡月號（Vend&eacute;miaire，F734）上月初穿越台灣海峽，引起中國不滿。<br />\n<a href=\"https://chinanews.co/news/gb/army/2019/05/201905012212.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchinanews.co%2Fnews%2Fgb%2Farmy%2F2019%2F05%2F201905012212.shtml&d=P2v3VPQ3iBAPr6cjv61qmU2FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=8d30656a\" target=\"_blank\">https://chinanews.co/news/gb/army/2019/05/201905012212.shtml</a>"},{"pid":"cd3d9c7296d6ae743d35e9655eda24518f41528b","tid":1134672,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T23:22:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">衰軟必輸，愈近愈豬！！</span></span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4e2494dce75c766441d875c8ea839a7b5f25562","tid":1134672,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T23:25:43.000Z","msg":"究竟台海係公海定中國內海？"},{"pid":"dd4d1108bfd4412e227c343a65febba0b44982c6","tid":1134672,"uid":61280,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T23:27:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>究竟台海係公海定中國內海？</blockquote><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">話明&quot;台海&quot;點會係支那呢？？？</span></span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dc610d7a4453967556723b1afd2757b9491c8d1","tid":1134672,"uid":77277,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"e4e2494dce75c766441d875c8ea839a7b5f25562","tid":1134672,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T23:25:43.000Z","msg":"究竟台海係公海定中國內海？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T23:35:07.000Z","msg":"美國內海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed29344d84fdcead83d378184a578b368acdb753","tid":1134672,"uid":7699,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T23:37:43.000Z","msg":"泰國都黎玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a516eac104462c96262dcdf28f5d41ed436921c4","tid":1134672,"uid":35790,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T23:40:26.000Z","msg":"期望明年大英祖國新航母經台海"},{"pid":"99506a8f22660a124a43f452523a9b8d29b7f880","tid":1134672,"uid":141151,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T23:44:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>秦軍返黎中原啦</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15430b53594f93b6aee16ef252c148fcfc8994d1","tid":1134672,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed29344d84fdcead83d378184a578b368acdb753","tid":1134672,"uid":7699,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T23:37:43.000Z","msg":"泰國都黎玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T23:48:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58c6015f308ac4d154809be684593bc80e71420f","tid":1134672,"uid":52477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T23:57:49.000Z","msg":"我大秦返來了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74a982ca929819baf74c90fe9ee1dc77ac194a33","tid":1134672,"uid":35790,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T00:01:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">「邦巴功」號護衛艦是中國製造的戰艦，根據中國053HT型護衛艦加以改良而成</span>，1989年動工、1990年7月25日下水，1991年7月20日正式服役。這艘戰艦滿載排水量1,924噸，配備4座雙聯裝「鷹擊」反艦導彈發射裝置、1座8管「西北風」艦空導彈發射裝置、2座中國雙100毫米主砲、8座雙37毫米副砲和2座5管固定式反潛深彈發射裝置。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">「邦巴功」號護衛艦與納萊頌恩號護衛艦（舷號421），上月21日抵達山東青島，參與解放軍海軍70年的海上閱兵，</span>在離開青島，邦巴功號護衛艦一路南下，穿越台灣海峽進入南海，前往湛江。​​​​ <br />\n<br />\n無得取參加消閱兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"583a7f2b636ecba8ec1a1bae1c99816dd702281c","tid":1134672,"uid":215225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T01:26:54.000Z","msg":"支那豬仲唔罷去泰國？"},{"pid":"42b74939e27a8b8f41b65d93f06fbaeb930c72bc","tid":1134672,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T01:35:37.000Z","msg":"經過香港以南海域，駛往廣東湛江，這是繼美國、法國軍艦之後，再有外國的軍艦駛經台灣海峽。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n行去中國點樣唔經中國水域<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果要話示威，應該全程唔停中國口岸，去韓國台灣日本途經台灣海峽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁先叫示威"},{"pid":"4579d15c59c114a4715274ed262cbd264a438b5b","tid":1134672,"uid":44646,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T01:36:32.000Z","msg":"連登仔高潮前應該先了解一下背景<br />\n<br />\n中國從無主張台海係內海/領海<br />\n外國軍艦駛經台海中國是否抗議<br />\n完全係對人不對事<br />\n<br />\n泰國軍艦在青島參加完中國海軍閱兵回國<br />\n走台海係最合理路線<br />\n呢件事應該早同北京打招呼<br />\n唔會有任何抗議<br />\n<br />\n近期最古怪既係法國<br />\n上次一樣係應邀去中國<br />\n由南太平洋出發，最合理一樣係走台海<br />\n<br />\n中國無抗議但取消邀請<br />\n斷估係最大可能係法艦行中線以西<br />\n姿態上可以被解釋為撐台灣"}]}